channel.title: Where is the best place to autofight?
channel.description:
Well where ever I try its impossible.
I tried cows, there to crowded and that messes the scripts up.
I tried goblins, but there colours match the ground or flags so the script/bot just starts clicking the wrong things.
I tried barabarians, but there is some talkable barabarians only and they just mess the bot up, there colours just match everythign around it, like their hair matches the fire etc...
SOOO...
What on earth do I auto on?!
